Ross Patterson, Mat Best, Jarred Taylor, and Evan Hafer invite the girl who volunteered to have a 72 hour date with JT on the show and scrutinize his every move.  Mat's wife then joins the show for a surprise drop-in on one of the wildest shows ever.  Drinks were flowing and we let it rip.
